  "game": {
    "title": "Relayer Advanced Definitive Edition",
    "description": "From the development team behind \"GOD WARS\" comes a new generation of robot SRPG to Nintendo Switch™ 2.\nThis is the complete version that includes the main game as well as all previously released DLC.\n\nCommand a unit of \"Stella Gear,\" humanoid weapons created using the technology of an ancient galactic civilization, and defend Earth from invasion by the mysterious lifeforms known as \"Relayer.\"\n\nThere are a total of approximately 100 cutscenes that are played when units battle each other.\n\nThe stage maps are also rendered in high-quality full 3D.\n\nThere is also \"Hate,\" which indicates how likely you are to be targeted by the enemy, a wide variety of skills, and special attacks such as the pincer attack \"Backstab\" and the special move \"Big Bang.\"\n\nUse a variety of strategies to lead the battle to victory.\n\nDLC included in this game\nTerra's Astoria NEXT\nSun's Amaterasu NEXT\nMercury's Petasos NEXT\nUranus's Herschel NEXT\nMilky Way's Galaxy Star NEXT\nHalley's Comet NEXT\nMintaka's Al-Jauza NEXT\nAlnilam's Epsilon NEXT\nAlnitak's Zeta NEXT\nMars's Neo Mars NEXT\nVenus's Amatsu-Mikaboshi NEXT\nLuna's Selene NEXT\nJupiter's Feretrius NEXT\nSaturn's Quadriga NEXT\nPluto's Tenmu Asuka NEXT\nNile's Dog Star NEXT\nEight's Trident NEXT\nSpin-Off Stories",
